{"tid":547791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大媽彌敦道人肉擋九巴 搞到巴士大排長龍","createTime":"2018-02-01T23:15:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-02T03:58:59.000Z","uid":160807,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0f09380785478116ce8cd88e77baa8098c349556","tid":547791,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T23:15:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180201/57782007\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180201%2F57782007&d=8FR%2FH2FOr0q1scos%2BgoAVozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=daad9fac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180201%2F57782007&h=d4b1c02d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180201/57782007</a><br />\n<br />\n彌敦道發生「大媽攔路」事件！事發於今日傍晚約6時，一部1A線的九巴由尖沙嘴總站駛出，當駛至彌敦道近油麻地永安的巴士站上落客後，剛駛離巴士站欲往太子方向行駛時，<span style=\"color: red;\">一名大媽突然跳出</span>，並站在車頭擋路拒絕離去。據現場目擊者稱，該女子疑因未能上車，心急下發難攔在車頭不讓巴士離開，車長須報警求助。<span style=\"color: red;\">不少尾隨的巴士亦因而無法埋站，大排長龍，造成彌敦道一度擠塞</span>。<br />\n「喂！行開啦！」「行開啦，咪阻住晒呀！」從目擊者陳小姐提供的片段可見，涉事的大媽年約50、60歲，戴眼鏡，穿上大衣及拿着手袋，站在九巴車頭前方，不斷與車長理論，其間不時有途人及車上乘客大叫「行開啦」，惟大媽卻拒絕離開，只逕自以不純正廣東話向車長喃喃地說，又指手劃腳。據陳小姐所知，「佢話架巴士開出後，就唔畀佢上車。」她認為該大媽做法不對，造成交通混亂：「上唔到咁等下一架囉，唔使擋住車頭唔畀人開車呀！」<br />\n而尾隨一部九巴亦因無法埋站被塞死，車長亦氣沖沖走上前與大媽理論：「人哋有規矩嘛，一離站就上唔到啦！」由於大媽堅持不肯走開，車長最後只好報警求助。<br />\n九巴發言人回應《蘋果》稱，晚上約6時30分，一部由尖沙嘴碼頭開出的1A線九巴駛至彌敦道近九龍中央郵政局時，一名女途人走出馬路，並站在巴士車頭前方阻礙巴士離開，事件擾攘數分鐘後，該名女途人自行返回行人路上，巴士其後繼續行車。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180201/large/1517489998_dc91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180201%2Flarge%2F1517489998_dc91.jpg&h=07671399&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10712f6a26e874b4b0ae10faea86f34e4a84fa15","tid":547791,"uid":21423,"like":23,"dislike":3,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T23:17:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ad15015535c9fc29e52a3681299daa0e2153d2c","tid":547791,"uid":43189,"like":1,"dislike":22,"score":-21,"quote":{"pid":"10712f6a26e874b4b0ae10faea86f34e4a84fa15","tid":547791,"uid":21423,"like":23,"dislike":3,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T23:17:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T23:20:40.000Z","msg":"師奶同大媽係兩樣嘢嚟"},{"pid":"d991789e255b853c840fe427aa0f6cd7c4257f59","tid":547791,"uid":21423,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T23:24:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5795b41560591e993cd5213b532b4fa990134f04","tid":547791,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T23:31:37.000Z","msg":"與強國接軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c725d3331dd9a68da305d3fcf7482c1f2e733168","tid":547791,"uid":47674,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"d991789e255b853c840fe427aa0f6cd7c4257f59","tid":547791,"uid":21423,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"6ad15015535c9fc29e52a3681299daa0e2153d2c","tid":547791,"uid":43189,"like":1,"dislike":22,"score":-21,"quote":{"pid":"10712f6a26e874b4b0ae10faea86f34e4a84fa15","tid":547791,"uid":21423,"like":23,"dislike":3,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T23:17:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T23:20:40.000Z","msg":"師奶同大媽係兩樣嘢嚟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T23:24:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T23:31:50.000Z","msg":"叫大媽有咩問題<br />\n支那啲公安你會唔會叫警察？"},{"pid":"0e3abdf02107b2c1be0d36f50193a8b68daddac2","tid":547791,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T23:35:47.000Z","msg":"鎖佢老母臭西啦，告佢公眾地方行為不檢"},{"pid":"5d3130818c7aba1d5537862f0